WEBVTT

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:10.000
The Preferences page allows you to view and update your user preferences.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:15.000
It includes five tabs: Profile, Roles, Time, Expense, and Password.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:29.000
The Passwords tab allows you to update your current password with a new one.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:36.000
It is highly recommended that all employees change their temporary passwords immediately upon logging into the web application.

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:39.000
Additionally, passwords expire every 60 days.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:44.000
You will receive a warning message 10 days before your password expires.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:46.000
These settings are designated by your organization.

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:52.000
If your password expires, please submit a Help Desk request to the IT department.

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:56.000
To change your password, type your current password in the Current Password field. 

00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:03.000
Next, type your new password in the New Password field and re-enter it in the Confirm Password field.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:08.000
Ensure that you follow your organization's guidelines for creating a strong password. 

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:11.000
Click the Save button to apply the change.